snippet.title: Reboot Develop
snippet.description:
The most high-end and unique game developers and games industry conference in Europe in it's fifth edition will be gathering absolutely top notch speaker lineup of 100+ speakers and more then 1500+ attendees!

It will be taking place from 19th to 21st of April 2018 in legendary city of Dubrovnik at luxurious Sheraton Dubrovnik resort.
